cz.syntea.xdef

Interface XDConstants

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SConstants

    public interface XDConstants
extends SConstants
    Constants used by X-definition builder. The constants with the name with the prefix "XDPROPERTY" are names of properties. The constants with the name with the prefix XDPROPERTYVALUE are valid values of respective property.
